             was indicted for <rs id="t17861213-3-off13" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17861213-3-off13" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17861213-3-off13" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17861213-3-cd14" type="crimeDate">10th day of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17861213-3-off13 t17861213-3-cd14"></join>, two pair of cotton stockings, value 6 s. 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17861213-3-victim45" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Smith
                        <interp inst="t17861213-3-victim45" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
